n: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://car.auto.ifeng.com/car/40242\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">2016款 1.2THP 自动精英型</a></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">15.19</td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">13.69&nbsp;<a class=\"inquiry\" title=\"2016款 1.2THP 自动精英型 报价\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(214, 0, 2); padding: 0px 2px;\">询价</a></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">1.50</td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">现车充足</td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://car.auto.ifeng.com/car/40461\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">2016款 1.6THP 自动领先型</a></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">15.19</td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">13.69&nbsp;<a class=\"inquiry\" title=\"2016款 1.6THP 自动领先型 报价\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(214, 0, 2); padding: 0px 2px;\">询价</a></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">1.50</td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: